ActYukon Act
SubjectPublic real properties located in Dawson City ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder transferring to the Government of Yukon, in perpetuity, the administration and control of public real properties identified as the Former Territorial Courthouse National Historic Site and the Red Feather Saloon reproduction building in the Dawson Historical Complex National Historic Site in the Yukon Territory.
